{
  "stem": "1721.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that point, Theresienstadt was not-- in '43, was not-- was not considered to be a death camp or a-- you know, it was considered to be sort of like a way station, the model camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know where I was going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother may have known, but I was not aware.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I may have been aware, but it didn't register to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this was at a train station in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the last thing he wanted was probably he didn't want an outbreak of jaundice, or yellow fever, or whatever else may have occurred right then and there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would have had a mess on their hands.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So whether it was kindness or it was just expeditious for him just to, you know, get rid of that source immediately, and just take care of that, and move everybody out.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think it was probably-- from his organized mind that was his thinking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think I was just probably just another patient there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I might have, but I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then we went to-- then we were-- we were loaded onto the-- when I left there, we were loaded onto the trains.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not Amtrak, I can tell you this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I didn't truly know that all those cattle cars that you see in the-- in the Holocaust museums were truly the ones.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I do remember being in one of those, and they were just disgusting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think I was with my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were all standing or sitting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were-- there were not seats.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
